          <comment xml:lang="en">The composition of an average industrial device was extracted from Tab 4.38 (ecoinvent v2.2 report 18_V). 88% steel, that was considered to have a C content of 0.012 (C content was calculated out of emission factors published in Commission Decision of 18 July 2007 establishing guidelines for the monitoring and reporting of greenhouse gas emissions pursuant to Directive 2003/87/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council (notified under document number C(2007) 3416)); 8% plastics (plastics C content was calculated using data in Tab A.2, ecoinvent v2.2 report 13_I); 3.2% PWB &amp; plugs (C content calculated using PWB composition)</comment>
